<br>
Ellrond 52 Wizard - Drinal            Neanderthall 50 Shaman <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugarielgrimfyre.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gariel Grimfyre</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/7/01 4:07:01 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Quest Spell trade in </span><hr size=1> It's completely random.  I've been trying to get Tishan's Discord for a while now by turning in various spells.  I've gotten 3 extra copies of Abscond and 2 extra copies of Thunderbold, but still no Tishan's. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
