 <p><b><i>Gariel Grimfyre</b></i>
<br><b><i>Level 52 Channeler of Solusek Ro</b></i></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uzealpath00.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ZealPath00</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_purplespot.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/7/01 5:50:59 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Quest Spell trade in </span><hr size=1> It's random, I got 2-3 Absconds per attempt to get other spells, so if Abscond is all you need then you'll get it within the first 2 scrolls I can almost guarantee you.<br>
<br>
I've managed to get all 4 of the spells (got discord when I was 51 and let me tell you that it's an absolutely excellent spell, well worth whatever number of scrolls it takes for you to get it), went through something like 10-12 trade-in scrolls before I got all of em tho. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uororo7.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ororo7</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/12/01 9:13:03 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Quest Spell trade in </span><hr size=1> What are people paying these days for trade-in spells?  Don't wanna go broke trying for Tishan's... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udaeanorendarion.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Daeanor Endarion</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.monmouth.com/~dhawthorne/everqst/picon.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/12/01 12:25:32 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.monmouth.com/~dhawthorne/everqst/ppic.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Quest Spell trade in </span><hr size=1> I will pay 100pp for a trade-in, no more. I sell (well, try to anyway, not much luck really) sell exras for the same. Someone asked for 1k for one of these reently and I laughed at them and refused to buy at that price. It's the only way to keep it reasonable - good chance you won't be getting what you want until many tries. <p><b>Daeanor Endarion of the Rathe</b></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showMessage?topicID=43.t